    "name": "Effect: Goo Grenade",
    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Goo Grenade (Lesser)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Goo Grenade (Moderate)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Goo Grenade (Greater)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Goo Grenade (Major)]</p>\n<p>When you hit a creature with a goo grenade, that creature takes persistent acid damage and a circumstance penalty to its Speeds from the clinging goo.</p>\n<p>The target can end any penalties, conditions, and persistent damage caused by the bomb by Escaping or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to pry themselves free of the ooze. These Interact actions don't have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.</p>"
